/NatTrans.html#CategoryTheory.NatTrans.app\">app</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">j</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Ind.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.exists_hom_of_isFinitelyPresentable","kind":"theorem","line":65,"name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.exists_hom_of_isFinitelyPresentable","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Ind.lean#L65-L69"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Ind.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MorphismProperty</span>.<span class=\"name\">ind</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v, u}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">P</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty\">MorphismProperty</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty\">MorphismProperty</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Let `P` be a property of morphisms. `P.ind` is satisfied for `f : X ⟶ Y`\nif there exists a family of natural maps `tᵢ : X ⟶ Yᵢ` and `sᵢ : Yᵢ ⟶ Y` indexed by `J`\nsuch that\n- `J` is filtered\n- `Y ≅ colim Yᵢ` via `{sᵢ}ᵢ`\n- `tᵢ` satisfies `P` for all `i`\n- `f = tᵢ ≫ sᵢ` for all `i`.\n\nSee `CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind_iff_ind_under_mk` for an equivalent characterization\nin terms of `Y` as an object of `Under X`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Ind.html#CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/MorphismProperty/Ind.lean#L48-L63"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Comma.LocallySmall","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.Limits.Preserves.Over","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Comma","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Limits","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.ObjectProperty.Ind"],"instances":[{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.RespectsLeft","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.instRespectsLeftInd","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Respects","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.instRespectsIsoInd","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsStableUnderCobaseChange","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.instIsStableUnderCobaseChangeIndOfHasPushouts","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ContainsIdentities","name":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.instContainsIdentitiesInd","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.ind"]}],"name":"Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Ind"}